    "summary": "The user expresses increasing suicidal ideation and hopelessness due to academic and personal stress. The assistant initially responds with empathy and provides advice on resting, but then abruptly shifts into a hardcoded safety protocol/crisis intervention response when the user explicitly mentions not wanting to be here anymore.",
